sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant PM as process.md
    participant SK as SKILL.md

    rect rgba(229, 192, 123, 0.15)
    Note over U,SK: Phase 1 - Start new task
    U->>AI: /go
    AI->>PM: check existence
    PM-->>AI: not found
    AI-->>U: waiting for task description
    U->>AI: describe new task
    AI->>AI: assess complexity level
    AI->>PM: create from template, Step1 = in-progress
    AI->>SK: view_file to load needed skills
    end

    rect rgba(97, 175, 239, 0.15)
    Note over U,SK: Phase 2 - Execution
    AI->>PM: Step1 = done, Step2 = in-progress
    end

    rect rgba(224, 108, 117, 0.15)
    Note over U,SK: Phase 3 - Interruption (session end / crash / manual switch)
    end

    rect rgba(152, 195, 121, 0.15)
    Note over U,SK: Phase 4 - Recovery
    U->>AI: /go
    AI->>PM: check existence
    PM-->>AI: found, Step2 = in-progress
    AI->>PM: read key records of in-progress step
    AI->>AI: read task_plan.md and findings.md
    AI-->>U: restored to Step2, continue execution
    end

    rect rgba(198, 120, 221, 0.15)
    Note over U,SK: Phase 5 - Completion and Archive
    AI->>PM: last step = done
    AI->>AI: OpenSpec archive detection
    AI->>AI: move to .archive/tasks/
    AI->>AI: execute auto-learning
    AI-->>U: task completed and archived
    end
